WEBVTT

00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:05.203
undzer intervyu. mir haltn yetst bay kasete numer tsvey. bite dertseyln zi vayter.

00:00:04.905 --> 00:00:08.240
oder antshuldikn zey, ikh ken in mitn iberraysn

00:00:08.348 --> 00:00:13.354
vos ikh hob nisht dertseylt, ven der daytsh iz arayn, undz ze'mir shoyn geven in shtot Boyberik

00:00:13.410 --> 00:00:15.817
iz nisht geven shtark vos tsu esn

00:00:15.823 --> 00:00:19.743
hobn mir ales getrogn farkoyfn un gegangen in di derfer

00:00:19.743 --> 00:00:21.303
un getoysht esn.

00:00:21.544 --> 00:00:23.920
un nisht eyn mol hot men undz gekhapt

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:27.203
di ukraynishe politsey, un m'hot ales tsugenumen oykhet bay undz

00:00:27.248 --> 00:00:31.353
iz dernokh dem flegn mir undz dray a zeyger bay nakht geyn

00:00:31.353 --> 00:00:34.663
ikh mit der shvester, az di ukraynishe politseyen hobn nokh geshlofn

00:00:34.740 --> 00:00:36.641
vos me flegt dort durkhgeyn

00:00:36.647 --> 00:00:38.328
flegn brengen a bisl esn

00:00:38.537 --> 00:00:41.467
iz baym sof hobn mir nisht gehat gornisht vos tsu toyshn

00:00:41.794 --> 00:00:45.250
iz geven zeyer a hunger. dos iz shoyn geven nokh peysekh.

00:00:45.250 --> 00:00:47.348
fleg ikh geyn oyf di felder

00:00:47.348 --> 00:00:50.447
un ikh f- oyf di felder fun di kartofl grobn

00:00:50.448 --> 00:00:53.532
iz geven a krokhmal, fun oyvn nokh di shney

00:00:53.532 --> 00:00:58.179
fleg ikh nemen dem krokhmal tsuzamennemen, fleg bakn fun dem pletslekh, un me fleg esn.

00:00:58.179 --> 00:01:00.208
un dos hot undz oyfgehaltn.

00:01:00.357 --> 00:01:03.112
dos iz geven vos ikh hob fargesn vos ikh hob nokh a mol geredt.

00:01:03.630 --> 00:01:04.707
yetst azoy

00:01:04.707 --> 00:01:06.774
vegn di BANDEROVTSes

00:01:06.128 --> 00:01:06.982
yo

00:01:06.774 --> 00:01:09.609
di BANDEROVTSes iz geven azoy. s'iz geven ukrayner

00:01:09.609 --> 00:01:12.402
vos zey hobn anfang mitgearbet mitn daytsh.

00:01:12.402 --> 00:01:14.469
zey hobn gevolt di eygene Ukrayne.

00:01:14.469 --> 00:01:19.419
oder ven der daytsh hot zey nisht gegebn di eygene Ukrayne, hobn zey gegangen gegn dem daytsh.

00:01:19.543 --> 00:01:21.410
es zenen arayn in di

00:01:21.552 --> 00:01:23.477
velder, un zenen gegangen

00:01:23.477 --> 00:01:27.717
un zey hobn d- geharget di daytshn, un zey hobn geharget di polyakn oykhet, yo?

00:01:27.778 --> 00:01:30.590
oder di ukrayner zen- hobn zey nisht getshepet.

00:01:31.677 --> 00:01:37.745
ven zey zenen gekumen ⟨demolstdike⟩ nakht tsu mir mit mayn khaverte, un mayn khaverte iz geven zeyer a ukraynke, yo?

00:01:37.887 --> 00:01:41.563
zi hot gevolt zeyer a sakh helfn di BANDERA, un ikh hob nisht gehat keyn breyre

00:01:41.563 --> 00:01:43.394
vayl ikh hob gemuzt zikh rateven

00:01:43.394 --> 00:01:46.233
afile s'iz mir geven nisht gut, nor ikh hob gemuzt zikh rateven.

00:01:46.999 --> 00:01:48.869
hot, hobn zey gezogt azoy.

00:01:48.869 --> 00:01:52.291
"undz veln mir dir gebn a retsept yod, zolst brengen a retsept

00:01:52.635 --> 00:01:56.859
un in Lemberik vet zayn aza adres. dort iz do ukraynishe politsey.

00:01:56.859 --> 00:02:00.791
du vest geyn tsu dem politsey un d'vest gebn dem retsept, keyner zol nisht zen

00:02:00.791 --> 00:02:02.973
un er vet ir shoyn ongreytn a pekele."

00:02:03.570 --> 00:02:07.428
un azoy iz geven. ikh bin gekumen Lemberik. ikh hob gegangen tsu dem sheygets

00:02:07.452 --> 00:02:10.669
un er hot mir ongegreyt a pekele, un ikh hob genumen dos pekele

00:02:11.130 --> 00:02:16.912
un undz ho'mir geshvartst di grenets mit dem. dos iz geven zeyer ayngeshtelt, vayl ven der daytsh khapt undz, harget men undz.

00:02:17.695 --> 00:02:20.554
hot undz gelungen etlekhe mol durkhtsufirn dos

00:02:20.554 --> 00:02:24.329
un zey hobn undz batsolt produktn farshidene zeyer gut. m'hot zeyer fardint

00:02:24.349 --> 00:02:26.514
un ikh hob mayn goye zeyer a sakh geholfn

00:02:26.824 --> 00:02:30.868
oder zi hot mir a sakh ge- geholfn oykhet. zi hot mir gevashn

00:02:30.925 --> 00:02:33.773
un zi hot mir ales, zi hot mir gefirt azoy vi a tokhter

00:02:33.773 --> 00:02:35.525
un ikh hob ir gegebn tsu esn.

00:02:36.156 --> 00:02:37.804
oder dernokh dem

00:02:37.860 --> 00:02:41.434
hot men ongehoybn vayter tsu shvartsn di ⟨gretn⟩ grenets

00:02:41.434 --> 00:02:45.262
un vayter zenen mir gegangen mit yod. m'hot genumen yod un di retsept.

00:02:45.522 --> 00:02:48.857
un eyn mol bay nakht geyen mir, shvartsn mir undz di grenets

00:02:49.453 --> 00:02:50.842
un di

00:02:50.842 --> 00:02:52.131
GESTAPO

00:02:52.508 --> 00:02:54.291
hot gegebn a farkhap undz

00:02:54.634 --> 00:02:57.170
un ikh hob gezen az ikh hob do dos pekele

00:02:57.170 --> 00:03:00.281
hob ikh laykhter dos gegebn a vorf avek vos zey hobn nisht bamerkt

00:03:00.456 --> 00:03:02.795
un me nemt undz. m'areshtirt undz.

00:03:02.835 --> 00:03:07.014
m'areshtirt undz un me firt undz tsun a shtot STOYANOV.

00:03:07.240 --> 00:03:09.309
in der tfise zetst men undz ayn.

00:03:09.552 --> 00:03:14.780
un ikh gedenk dos azoy haynt vos ikh vel keyn mol nisht fargesn vos s'iz geven a daytsh

00:03:14.780 --> 00:03:17.665
er hot yener gezogt "DAS iz EIN JUDE" oyf mir.

00:03:17.665 --> 00:03:19.823
ot dos hot er gegebn a zog.

00:03:19.963 --> 00:03:23.332
oder ikh hob zikh nisht gemakht visndik KEILU er meynt nisht mir.

00:03:23.389 --> 00:03:24.817
kh'hob zikh gemakht nisht visndik.

00:03:25.296 --> 00:03:27.382
s'iz dokh alts geven bashert tsu lebn.

00:03:27.777 --> 00:03:31.466
shpeter azoy. ikh hob nisht, antshuldikt mikh zeyer vos ikh hob gekhapt

00:03:31.557 --> 00:03:34.048
vos ikh hob aykh nisht dertseylt vegn mayn mamen.

00:03:34.982 --> 00:03:37.980
ven di, der daytsh iz arayn

00:03:38.020 --> 00:03:41.006
in di b- MISHTARA, dos hob ikh ⟨aykh nisht⟩ dertseylt UNK?

00:03:41.006 --> 00:03:43.203
oh, dos vil ikh yetst dertseyln.

00:03:43.369 --> 00:03:46.118
eyder m'hot, ⟨vi⟩ ikh bin antlofn

00:03:46.118 --> 00:03:47.921
iz di mame gelign krank

00:03:47.921 --> 00:03:51.035
vayl dem bruder hot men oyfgehongen, hot zi zeyer a sakh ibergelebt

00:03:51.035 --> 00:03:53.373
hot zi mir gerufn tsum bet

00:03:53.373 --> 00:03:54.607
un zi hot mir gezogt

00:03:54.607 --> 00:03:58.373
"mayn kind, du bist mayn beste kind. du antloyf in dorf arayn

00:03:58.444 --> 00:04:01.743
un ikh vel oyf dir oysbetn vu du vest lebn blaybn."

00:04:01.743 --> 00:04:04.361
dos hob ikh fargesn vos ikh antshuldik zikh, yo

00:04:04.361 --> 00:04:05.456
dos iz geven.

00:04:05.492 --> 00:04:07.371
un vu ikh bin gegangen

00:04:07.371 --> 00:04:09.903
hob ikh geklert "mayn mame hit mir op."

00:04:09.913 --> 00:04:12.520
un ikh UNK nokh dem zeyer gegleybt a sakh

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:16.095
vayl ikh bin zeyer fun a frumer shtub, un ikh hob gevust zeyer a sakh z- yidishkeyt.

00:04:17.153 --> 00:04:19.239
azoy, mikh hot men gekhapt

00:04:19.279 --> 00:04:22.026
un ikh hob shoyn gornisht nisht gehat, nor vos iz?

00:04:22.026 --> 00:04:26.489
leydik bin ikh geven, vos ikh hob ales avekgevorfn, un ikh hob moyre gehat vos er hot gezogt

00:04:26.489 --> 00:04:27.727
"EIN JUDE"

00:04:27.767 --> 00:04:30.312
oder m'hot zikh dernokh dem nisht visndik gemakht.

00:04:30.312 --> 00:04:34.573
m'hot mikh arayngefirt in a tfise, un undz ze'mir dort gezesn in tfise

00:04:34.573 --> 00:04:36.116
dos gedenk ikh nisht vifl.

00:04:36.542 --> 00:04:39.914
fun der tfise in eyn tog hot men undz gefirt keyn Lemberik.

00:04:39.914 --> 00:04:42.698
s'iz geven mer, nisht nor undz aleyn. s'iz geven mer.

00:04:42.698 --> 00:04:44.799
m'hot undz gebrengt keyn Lemberik

00:04:44.799 --> 00:04:47.096
un m'hot undz gegebn in a lager

00:04:47.096 --> 00:04:48.957
nisht in a tfise nor in a lager.

00:04:48.957 --> 00:04:51.600
vos iz geven der lager? der lager iz geven

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:54.069
vos di yunge ukraynishe

00:04:54.278 --> 00:04:57.255
shikses hobn badorfn forn keyn Daytshland tsu der arbet

00:04:57.255 --> 00:05:01.084
azoy m- dos hot men gegebn dem shtrof vos me hot undz gekhapt oyf der grenets.

00:05:02.142 --> 00:05:05.477
azoy ikh hob badorfn forn mit mayn khaverte keyn Daytshland

00:05:05.702 --> 00:05:08.939
hot men badorfn zikh makhn peser az ikh bin a ukraynke.

00:05:08.939 --> 00:05:09.977
far vos?

00:05:09.977 --> 00:05:16.477
vayl di, di ukrayner hobn nisht badorfn trogn keyn P. di polyakn hobn badorfn ⟨trign⟩ kr- trogn a P.

00:05:16.477 --> 00:05:20.211
oyfn hartsn, iz zey geven a sakh erger vi di ukrayner in Daytshland.

00:05:21.008 --> 00:05:26.503
hot men gezogt, do iz do a ukraynisher politsyan- d- heyst di politsyantn, di onfirers

00:05:26.526 --> 00:05:30.873
iz zey makhn dem. zey farhern vi azoy zey gibn aroys di papirn.

00:05:31.588 --> 00:05:34.386
az ikh bin tsugegangen tsu di ukrayner

00:05:34.386 --> 00:05:36.572
un ikh hob gezen vos zey fregn

00:05:36.572 --> 00:05:40.189
hot dos mir nisht gefoln. far vos? zey hobn gefregt vi azoy in kloyster

00:05:40.262 --> 00:05:42.570
zey hobn gefregt di tsen gebot

00:05:42.570 --> 00:05:45.805
dos vos ikh hob nisht gevust, un ikh bin in kloyster keyn mol nisht geven

00:05:45.810 --> 00:05:48.294
hob ikh moyre gehat tsutsugeyn tsu zey

00:05:48.294 --> 00:05:50.124
kedey ikh zol zikh makhn papirn.

00:05:50.370 --> 00:05:53.463
nor ikh hob geklert azoy. ikh muz fun dem lager antloyfn.

00:05:53.463 --> 00:05:55.388
un nokh a mol vet men mikh khapn

00:05:55.388 --> 00:05:56.695
vi azoy s'zol nisht zayn

00:05:56.695 --> 00:05:58.515
vel ikh shoyn di papirn makhn.

00:05:59.803 --> 00:06:03.361
iz farn na- s'iz geven bay nakht, dakht zikh. ikh shtey oyf

00:06:03.361 --> 00:06:05.602
un s'iz geven arum un arum drotn

00:06:06.165 --> 00:06:09.463
un ikh hob genumen oyf di drotn, ikh hob gekrokhn

00:06:09.463 --> 00:06:11.208
ikh hob gegebn a shpring ariber

00:06:11.208 --> 00:06:17.144
un dos iz geven. di mame hot mikh opgehitn vos keyner, di daytshn ⟨zenen nokh⟩ arumgegangen mit di biksn, un keyner hot mikh nisht gezen.

00:06:17.404 --> 00:06:20.877
un ikh antloyf, un ikh tserays dos gantse kleyd hintn

00:06:20.877 --> 00:06:22.258
hob ikh tserisn

00:06:23.226 --> 00:06:26.294
un dos iz geven in ovnt, un ikh kum tsu mayn goye.

00:06:26.294 --> 00:06:31.694
ikh kum tsu mayn goye, zogt zi "vos iz geshen? du bist gezesn ⟨umedum⟩. ikh hob moyre gehat az du bist a yidishe.

00:06:31.694 --> 00:06:34.121
ale shkheynim zogn az du bist a yidishe."

00:06:34.532 --> 00:06:39.372
zog ikh "ikh bin nisht keyn yidishe" zog ikh "kh'hob antlofn. ikh hob badorfn makhn papirn" zog ikh "yetst vil ikh

00:06:39.372 --> 00:06:42.929
zen in mayn dorf aroysnemen fun dortn, ikh zol makhn papirn."

00:06:43.341 --> 00:06:44.769
zogt zi "yo, gut."

00:06:44.910 --> 00:06:46.527
un ikh hob ongehoybn tsu forn.

00:06:46.527 --> 00:06:48.940
nor vos? ikh hob shoyn gezen me zol mir khapn

00:06:48.940 --> 00:06:50.423
oyf der grenets

00:06:50.648 --> 00:06:55.620
⟨ze'mir⟩ undz ze'mir geforn d- oyf der grenets, un m'hot geshvartst di grenets, un ikh hob shoyn gornisht gehat

00:06:55.710 --> 00:06:59.824
un di daytshn vayter khapn undz. ikh hob shoyn gezen vi di daytshn zoln undz khapn.

00:06:59.824 --> 00:07:01.526
zey hobn undz gekhapt

00:07:02.190 --> 00:07:03.382
beyde

00:07:03.743 --> 00:07:06.066
un zey hobn undz genumen tsu

00:07:06.223 --> 00:07:11.701
dos iz SOKOLOV geheysn tsi, ikh gedenk nisht, UNK SOKOLOVer tfise

00:07:11.826 --> 00:07:14.590
un ikh bin dort gezesn oykhet a por vokhn.

00:07:14.590 --> 00:07:17.794
in der tfise zenen mir aroysgegangen oyfn feld arbetn.

00:07:18.019 --> 00:07:20.985
es iz undz geven shver. m'hot geshlofn oyf shteyner

00:07:20.985 --> 00:07:24.336
vos hobn mir gehat bay zikh hobn mir zikh tsugedekt mit der khaverte.

00:07:24.336 --> 00:07:27.091
dort iz geven zeyer a sakh ukraynkes. nor vos iz?

00:07:27.091 --> 00:07:29.809
ikh hob shoyn demolts gekent zeyer gut di shprakh

00:07:29.967 --> 00:07:36.255
un ikh hob shoyn gekent zeyere modlitves, hob ikh nokh gekent fun shule, vos ikh hob gegangen in shule, hob ikh gekent di modlitves oykhet

00:07:36.379 --> 00:07:41.351
un yedn in der fri hob ikh ge- geknit, un ikh hob gezogt di modlitves, azoy keyner zol nisht

00:07:41.391 --> 00:07:43.359
meynen az ikh bin a yidishe.

00:07:43.838 --> 00:07:47.882
s'hot gedoyert a por vokhn, a por monat, dos ken ikh nisht visn

00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:49.924
vos me kumt meldn

00:07:49.924 --> 00:07:56.381
az yetst nemt men undz tsurik keyn Lemberik in dem lager, un undz darfn mir forn keyn Daytshland, arbetn keyn Daytshland. dos vet vayter zayn di shtrof.

00:07:57.372 --> 00:08:04.976
me nemt undz eyn tog, un me fort keyn Lemberik, un ikh kum keyn Lemberik. ikh ze di gas vu ikh hob gevoynt. ikh kuk zikh um, ikh tref nisht keynemen

00:08:05.877 --> 00:08:07.940
un me kumt in dem zelbn lager.

00:08:07.940 --> 00:08:10.072
in dem zelbn lager kumt men

00:08:10.230 --> 00:08:14.156
un ikh kuk nor um. ikh hob moyre zol emetser trefn vos me ken mikh

00:08:14.888 --> 00:08:20.096
un tsvishn dem yo iz geven eyne a ukraynke vos hot mikh gekent. dos iz nokh geven far dem.

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:22.543
zi hot mir gevolt oysgebn.

00:08:23.055 --> 00:08:25.959
far dem iz dokh nokh geven. hot zi mir genumen

00:08:25.959 --> 00:08:30.512
oyf plats KRAKOWSKI, un zi hot gezogt "du veyst vos? du muzst mir zogn vu du voynst. ikh vel dikh yetst

00:08:30.512 --> 00:08:31.385
oysgebn."

00:08:31.797 --> 00:08:36.803
hob ikh zi farfirt tsvishn mentshn. ikh hob zikh gegebn a rays aroys. ikh hob antlofn. dos iz geven anfang.

00:08:36.960 --> 00:08:38.366
kh'hob antlofn

00:08:38.366 --> 00:08:40.644
un keyner hot nisht gevust. keyner hot nisht gezen.

00:08:40.644 --> 00:08:41.459
yo?

00:08:41.549 --> 00:08:44.356
dernokh dem, ven, in dem, dem lager ven m'iz gekumen

00:08:44.356 --> 00:08:45.881
hot men vayter gemoldn

00:08:46.022 --> 00:08:49.006
"ver s'iz a ukraynke zol tsugeyn in dem komitet

00:08:49.006 --> 00:08:50.555
un makhn zikh papirn."

00:08:51.642 --> 00:08:54.234
un ikh gey tsu tsu dem komitet

00:08:54.527 --> 00:08:57.620
un tsvishn dem bin ikh dokh gegangen in kloyster

00:08:57.620 --> 00:08:58.642
oykhet

00:08:58.642 --> 00:09:02.852
un mayn goye hot mikh oysgelernt di tsen gebot.

00:09:02.852 --> 00:09:04.236
fun anfang

00:09:04.236 --> 00:09:07.076
biz sof, di tsen gebot hob ikh gevust.

00:09:07.369 --> 00:09:09.656
ikh gey tsu tsu dem komitet

00:09:09.656 --> 00:09:13.146
zitst eyner, zogt er "fun vanet bistu?" zog ikh "ikh bin fun VILKHOVETS."

00:09:13.146 --> 00:09:14.220
OLCHOWCE.

00:09:14.507 --> 00:09:17.516
"oy" zogt er. "ikh hob dokh dortn a bakante" zogt er.

00:09:17.516 --> 00:09:21.099
zog ikh "yo, ir man iz geharget gevorn in di milkhome. kh'hob zi gekent."

00:09:21.797 --> 00:09:24.941
zogt er azoy "veyst vos? gib ikh papirn."

00:09:24.941 --> 00:09:27.595
zitst dort a tsveyter sheygets, un er zogt azoy

00:09:27.595 --> 00:09:29.520
"neyn, zol zi nokh eyn frage zogn."

00:09:29.880 --> 00:09:31.708
zog ikh "vos iz di frage?"

00:09:31.708 --> 00:09:33.066
zogt er "veyst vos?

00:09:33.066 --> 00:09:36.540
zog di naynte tsen gebot" tsu mir azoy.

00:09:36.748 --> 00:09:39.290
azoy er hot gezogt di naynte tsen gebot

00:09:39.432 --> 00:09:41.640
fun anfang biz sof hob ikh gevust.

00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:43.236
di naynte hob ikh nisht gevust.

00:09:43.236 --> 00:09:45.694
iz geshtanen hinter mir emetser

00:09:45.694 --> 00:09:47.513
un m'hot mir gegebn a zog unter

00:09:47.513 --> 00:09:49.587
"ganve nisht in Daytshland."

00:09:49.587 --> 00:09:50.816
hob ikh gegebn a zog

00:09:51.227 --> 00:09:52.472
"NE KRADY

00:09:52.472 --> 00:09:55.406
V GERMANI" ikh hob gegebn a zog "ganve nisht in Daytshland."

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:57.139
un dos hot zey zeyer gefoln.

00:09:57.139 --> 00:10:00.885
zogt er azoy. "veyst vos? ikh ken, ikh ken dir

00:10:00.885 --> 00:10:02.353
f- di meydl.

00:10:02.353 --> 00:10:05.193
git aroys papirn, zol zi geyn makhn bilder

00:10:05.301 --> 00:10:06.864
un git aroys papirn.

00:10:06.955 --> 00:10:08.141
gey makh bilder."

00:10:08.141 --> 00:10:10.067
ikh hob tsugegangen. ikh hob gemakht bilder.

00:10:10.067 --> 00:10:15.226
ikh gedenk nisht vi azoy, tsi ikh hob gehat di gelt, tsi er hot mir batsolt far di, far di bilder. dos gedenk ikh nit

00:10:15.325 --> 00:10:18.460
un ikh hob gemakht tsvey bilder. ikh hob tsugegangen dortn

00:10:18.460 --> 00:10:24.397
un m'hot mir gegebn a dokument mit a zigl umedum "GREKO-KATOLICHKA" iz geshtanen geshribn in dem.

00:10:24.876 --> 00:10:30.776
